    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171380/extras/2ee6126948e65a24c7a4886027b4f8cd.avif?t=1770012285\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171380/extras_big/2ee6126948e65a24c7a4886027b4f8cd.webp?t=1770012285 width=1560 height=319 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get stupid &amp; get stupid weapons. Kill your friends to WIN BIG!!! Shenaniguns is a silly, frantic top-down multiplayer shooter, with tons of unique guns and items in a randomizer. No time to think! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 120+ weapons such as </strong>pistols, shotguns, snipers, grenades, turrets, portal guns, concentrated uranium, grappling hooks, 4&quot; tungsten cubes, industrially sized water guns, gasoline, pepper spray, gambling, galvanized square steel, drones, RPGs... <strong>and much, much more, including special abilities and enchantments!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171380/extras/dc36b9c8ba16bd77b1e3e8398df3ed01.avif?t=1770012285\" width=800 height=195 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free for all</strong> - Kill as many people as possible!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team deathmatch</strong> - Two even teams, red and blu!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 Weapons</strong> - Wow! 1/120th extra chance to get more tungsten cubes!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Capture the flag</strong> - Capture the other team's flag for extra points!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Capture the point</strong> - Stand on points around the map to gain points for your team!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss battles</strong> - Vectah, Trixie, and Spy! Get achievements &amp; lots of mark bucks for beating them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gun gaem</strong> - Your weapons you get are tied to your points, and everyone starts with the same items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DROP</strong> - Drop your item when you die, pick up others to make a loadout!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHAOS</strong> - Explode when you die, move faster, 3 weapons, closer spawning, bigger fires, bigger battles, and a whole lot of nuclear waste</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CLANK</strong> - Make them <i>WIREBACKS</i> drink <i>WATER</i>! Beat up hordes of <u><i><strong>CLANKERS</strong></i></u>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171380/extras/0b8334f439a46c397f8ed37edbd81d0c.avif?t=1770012285\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's<strong> 50</strong>-ish skins to customize!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Private servers</strong> where you can spawn 20 vectahs and blow the entire place to smithereens!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice chat</strong> so you can, optionally, get yelled at in public lobbies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A completely custom OST</strong> you can blast your eardrums out whilst you blast your friends... away...?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Did I mention there there are<strong> 20</strong> maps? <u><i><strong>You like numbers don't you. </strong></i></u>You love it when I say all of these big numbers, don't you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trust me, even if you can't comprehend the MAGNITUDE of these values, it means there's a LOT of content. Wowee.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What are you waiting for? What are you waiting for? What are you waiting for?</p>",
